1. *Luda* nedelja (Crazy week).
2. Zbog *ludog* stresa, nisam mogla da spavam (Because of crazy stress, I couldn't sleep).
3. Ona je postala *luda* od sreće (She became crazy with happiness).
4. *Ludo* sam se zaljubila u njega (I fell madly in love with him).
5. *Ludilo* se širi (Madness is spreading).